        <briefdescription>
<para>Peek at data written to virtual serial port. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Reads the data without consuming it. Future calls to <ref refid="serial__test_8h_1a1e2a3d82504b34d5b4590afc67172c9e" kindref="member">serial_vnd_peek_out_data()</ref> or <ref refid="serial__test_8h_1ab9b60bf8d62db2be3ad530cd0a78aedd" kindref="member">serial_vnd_read_out_data()</ref> will return this data again. Requires CONFIG_RING_BUFFER.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="warning"><para>Use cases involving multiple reads of the data must prevent concurrent read operations, either by preventing all readers from being preempted or by using a mutex to govern reads.</para>
</simplesect>
